sections.content:
“Perbadanan  Pembangunan  Bandar”  means  the  Perbadanan 
Pembangunan   Bandar   established   under   the   *Perbadanan 
Pembangunan  Bandar  Act  1971  [Act  46];

“vested”,    in    relation    to    property,    includes    rights    to  
property  which    are    future    or    contingent    and    rights    in  
reversion   and remainder;

(a) be  issued  or  allotted  at  such  times  and  on  such  terms, 
as to   allotment,   as   the   Minister   of   Finance   may,  
after consultation  with  the  Minister  direct;
